1. Commit all changes to git main branch
2. ssh into server
3. git pull on server
4. navigate to 'frontend' folder
5. npm install
6. execute 'npm run build'
7. kill previous pm2 daemon via 'pm2 kill'
8. start frontend with pm2 daemon 'pm2 serve build 40593 --spa'
9. navigate to backend folder
10. npm install
11. verify that .env file is in place
12. pm2 start [main backend file]

When necessary:
13. redeploy database data definition file for fresh db